1.
Tompo malala o! henoy 
Borahiko aminao
Ireo tsiambarateloko 
Miankohoka aminao 
Inty re mitalaho 
Miaiky aho f’efa diso Aminao
1.1:
Miantsoantso aho
Fa tery am-panahy
Zao vao tsapako fa lavitra Anao 
Inty re miondrika aho 
Te hitoetra anilanao aho 
Fa eo an-tanambokovoko 
No hitalahon’I foko 
Raha mety Hianao Jeso
2.
Eny ry Tompo Jeso 
Nangirifiry anao ‘lay hazo nijalianao 
Ka nividiananao lay jamba tahaka ahy 
Mba ahita hazavana indray
2.1:
Inona e no tsy nanaovako Anao 
Izay mety ho ratsy no efa natao 
Zarako aza mbola miaina
Fa tsy maty very maina
Fa soa Hianao tsy nanadino
Ity fo tsy nety nino Navotanao Jeso
